{"tid":467412,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"﻿Stephy謝票送抱益影迷","createTime":"2017-11-13T13:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T13:25:58.000Z","uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c3f97df5af9bf64fc2de4ee04b1bf47e7853992c","tid":467412,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T13:15:59.000Z","msg":"鄧麗欣（Stephy）和樂基兒等台前幕後，前晚出席合演新片《女士復仇》首映禮，眾人更進入戲院向觀眾謝票，Stephy更與幸運影迷擁抱。<br />\n<br />\nStephy坦言要同時宣傳《女》片及另一部電影《空手道》，感到「左右做人難」及有點尷尬。有指杜汶澤執導的《空》片入場率不高，Stephy 認為票房不代表電影的成敗，入場觀眾口碑最重要，暫時的評價頗高，故她認為已是成功，Stephy道：「杜汶澤可能會覺得對我唔住，我覺得唔關事，我哋覺得已經係成功，我有同佢講，佢喺我心目中係才華橫溢嘅！」<br />\n<br />\n樂基兒則透露，她的老公將約朋友入場欣賞《女》片，她亦坦言，老公明白是工作需要，不會介意她性感演出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/211457_12704eb9804827906a11d54c457651b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F211457_12704eb9804827906a11d54c457651b7.jpg&h=e7304471&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/211513_051687384b8d7e44ac17bda442fb028e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F211513_051687384b8d7e44ac17bda442fb028e.jpg&h=eb4bda82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"940590a4d45485ab544922f7824cb7bbfadec7b4","tid":467412,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T13:25:58.000Z","msg":"後抱得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}